data.description: A True Gem in Canton  Welcome to this gorgeous and fully renovated 3 bedrooms/2 bathrooms  home in a quiet, established, amenity  neighborhood in Sequoyah district.  This house has almost everything newer, less than 3 years old. Move in Ready home. One level home with large flat front and back. Newer roof, windows, flooring, appliances, spray foam insulation, HVAC, Beautiful Cabinets and concrete countertops. Newer Bathrooms Brand new septic, too. Large level lot with large outbuilding in backyard, A perfect house to be called Home. This beautiful home won't be last so hurry up.
